Probably because the other one was compressed.
- as in PDFs can be compressed themselves. They are called "compressed PDFs" and are just the .pdf file probably with either lower quality or more direct text commands.

It's 20MB because the pages are scanned, not OCR'd.
The other ones are just text, which is much smaller in size, and the text can be searched, not like this one.
